WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Step 1: Paste or upload the job posting.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Step 2: Analyze the requirements and search evidence across saved CV variants.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Step 3: Match profile evidence to the role and build a custom CV.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Step 4: Use profile knowledge, the posting, and personal details to draft a cover letter.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.000
Step 5: Generate both documents, run ATS checks, and review the illustrative score.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Step 6: Optionally save the tailored CV as a new knowledge-base variant.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Step 7: Download the tailored CV and cover letter directly as separate PDFs.
